window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>The Vainqueur the Dragon Complete Series Bundle is 4 full books of a LitRPG adventure about an arrogant dragon and his unlucky sidekick on their quest to become the world's richest adventurers.</b></p> <p>Vainqueur Knightsbane is your average dragon: a giant, fire-breathing lizard who loves to take naps on his golden hoard, kidnap princesses for fun, and make the life of adventurers miserable. Vainqueur's only pleasure in life is to watch his treasure get bigger, one coin at a time.</p> <p>So when a would-be thief turned unwilling minion tells him about \"classes,\" \"levels,\" and \"quests,\" Vainqueur wonders if maybe, just maybe, he should consider a career change.</p> <p>After all, why bother hunting monsters for free when you can get paid for it?</p> <p><b>Experience this special edition LitRPG box set of Vainqueur the Dragon, by Maxime J. Durand, bestselling author of Apocalypse Tamer and The Perfect Run. Full of equal parts action and laughs, this story is a satirical take on the typical LitRPG and Isekai plot with an hilarious twist.</b></p>"; 
